HEADWORD: Honshu
<hw>Hon"shu</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <ety>[Jap.]</ety> <def>the main
island of Japan. Together with the islands of Hokkaido, Kyushu and
Shikoku it forms the bulk of the land area of Japan.</def>⟦br⟧
